                "latex": "\\frac{BD}{DC} = \\frac{S_{\\triangle ABD}}{S_{\\triangle ACD}} = \\frac{S_{\\triangle OBD}}{S_{\\triangle OCD}} = \\frac{S_{\\triangle ABD}-S_{\\triangle OBD}}{S_{\\triangle ACD}-S_{\\triangle OCD}} = \\frac{S_C}{S_B}"
